{"tid":1925302,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以色列發明左武漢肺炎疫苗 不過","createTime":"2020-03-14T09:39:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T17:46:13.000Z","uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a91a139750fb047839b9308b04c21c335e630021","tid":1925302,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:39:22.000Z","msg":"‪Israeli research center to announce it developed coronavirus vaccine, sources say - Israel News - <a href=\"http://Haaretz.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FHaaretz.com&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=67a6fe65\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Haaretz.com</a><br />\n<br />\n要排期做人體試驗<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-coronavirus-vaccine-israel-biological-research-institute-develope-1.8665074‬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2F.premium-coronavirus-vaccine-israel-biological-research-institute-develope-1.8665074%E2%80%AC&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCTcyzTZykTUlxRhnZlW9F%2Bg%3D&h=d487863b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/.premium-coronavirus-vaccine-israel-biological-research-institute-develope-1.8665074‬</a><br />\n<br />\nAround a month and a half after the genetic sequence was published, biotechnology company Moderna, Inc., based in Boston, Massachussets, announced it had completed the development of a possible coronavirus vaccine. Immediately afterward the vaccine was sent to the U.S. National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases, with clinical trials, which will include up to 25 health participants, to start in April and end in the summer. Any Israel vaccine will presumably also need to go through a similar or even stricter process before it will be approved for use."},{"pid":"ee7a3bb80bc3d1510c8081dcecb4ecde64fbf3b7","tid":1925302,"uid":125168,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T09:40:4